title: The Latinx Vote Comes Of Age
description: For the first time in election history, Latinos are projected to be the second-largest voting demographic in the country. The reason? Gen Z Latinx voters, many of whom are casting a ballot for the first time in 2020. So we asked a bunch of them:  Who do you plan to vote for? What issues do you care about? And what do you want the rest of the country to know about you?
